    • Method Detail

      • process

        void process(OptionProcessingContext processingContext)

        Processes the Entry<Option<?>, Object> contained in the passed OptionProcessingContext, using the processor associated with the Option.

        Parameters:
        processingContext - Holder for all information needed during the option processing.
        Throws:
        com.github.dandelion.core.DandelionException - if something goes wrong during the processing of the option value.

      • isBundleGraphUpdatable

        boolean isBundleGraphUpdatable()
        Returns:
        true if the option being processed can update the bundle graph, false otherwise.
